data.description: Welcome to your dream home nestled on picturesque 5.4-acres! This stunning 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath residence offers a serene retreat from the hustle and bustle of everyday life. Immerse yourself in luxury and comfort as you explore the incredible features of this meticulously maintained abode. Upon entering, you'll be captivated by the grandeur of the vaulted living room ceiling, adorned with exquisite, exposed beams. The spacious and airy atmosphere creates a sense of openness and tranquility, perfect for relaxation or entertaining guests. Natural light pours in through the large windows, illuminating the space and accentuating its beauty. The master suite is a true oasis, boasting a generous floor plan and an indulgent master bathtub and walk-in shower that beckon you to unwind and melt away the stress of the day. Plenty of cleared out space for a shop or other outbuildings. Partially bordered by USFS land. Call Helen Goucher at 406-334-9502, or your real estate professional.
